Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm working hard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a full-fledged draker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to learn a lot of\Nnew things every day, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your arms more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to hold your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you shoot real bullets just yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but keep practicing every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, on point!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we don't need more, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Well, aren't you starting to\Nlook the part!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be a newbie forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Mika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the bridge to bring the ship closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get good oil from this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't jump on it again, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, why does he always...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Draking vessel, Quin Zaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place I belong to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:02:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, can you fit some more there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tired?\N-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been extracting oil for\N48 hours straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot, smelly and we're covered in soot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, what a place you've ended up in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you always look like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, to be young...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll arrive to a big town in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When we deliver all this oil to the\Nrefinery company over there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be able to relax for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One last effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeeeeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If we sell all this,\Nhow much will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a lot of good oil this time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs-san, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you think it will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are dragons that valuable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"One dragon makes seven towns flourish",\Nthey say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat and oil go without saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but depending on the species, the bones\Ncan become craft products,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and entrails can be materials for medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons are mountains of treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the loss when we fail to capture one\Nis huge, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Draking vessels are a money hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, even with this, we're in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how much would...\Nmy compensation be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Only... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita-san, since you still owe your entrance\Npay to the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what's being substracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have it hard too, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's obvious, but was there\Nstill that much left?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta work hard to pay it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, give me some oil cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you dry and dehidratate it,\Nyou can get some good broth from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can simply boil it and\Neat it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have it hard too, Mika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a passenger ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The town must be close...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure gets cold really fast outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That scared me! A bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, birds shouldn't fly this high...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be a...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... we're finally done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah...\N-I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you gonna do when we land?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Goes without saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Booze, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky has dragons! The land has booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! A small one has sneaked\Ninto the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Takita, leave it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're worn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! You rest too, Takita.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Um... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons are a mountain of treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takita.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did it go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, this is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, why are you\Nfollowing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No particular reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, are you snitching food again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Indeed" you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You were attacked? What bit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a mouse, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a dog or a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Gibbs collapsed!\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he got bit by something weird\Nand collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Something weird? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Takita?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't found it yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We are searching everywhere\Non the ship but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... it escaped outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to find it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incomparable to any bird or beast\Naround there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, explain what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's with the ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Vannie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Gibbs collapsed, apparently.\N-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? It's Takita.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A small dragon?\NAnd you say it ran inside the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... it stopped on the deck's handrail...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I noticed, it had jumped inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell us immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everyone was so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought "I can deal with this myself!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say it's venomous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a dragon like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you wanted to catch it alone and\Nget a good chunk of money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I may or may not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, was it about this size?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,About this... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a dragon this small!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we split in groups and catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah!\N-I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go tell the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-No...\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It has either poison or a virus...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're not careful and end up\Nwith more people infected, it'd be for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What should we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we solve it,\Nwe should gather all in one place
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and select a few people to catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... it's as Jiro says.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who should go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's already in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't rest assured with just those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's small we don't need strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have good eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Can we leave it to you?\N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it have to be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The bridge is in the furthest end\Nof the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing we can do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Berko! That's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? It's my lifeline!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How long it's been since we took her in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,About three months, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thing sure aren't boring since Takita arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, do you smell any dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of dragon oil is adhered\Nto the ship and my body
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's the only thing I smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly want some fried food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't mistake it, Takita?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs-san was actually attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, dragons don't get close to ships\Non their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it attracted by something...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably this smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon oil...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that it gets closer to dragons\Nbigger than it relying on their smell
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and parasitizes on them to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of different dragons, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragons we know are just a small part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, this guy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oops...\N-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-This little...\N-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! Don't let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If it bites, the poison will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the one that bit Gibbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I see such a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, are you really going to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know if it's venomous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come crying if you get poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine as long as I don't eat the entrails.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we were lucky we could solve it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Newbie, don't go off on your own too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel! You're a newcomer too, Jiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a full-fledged crew member already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump me with someone who joined\Nfor no particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You've learned to talk big, eh, Jiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey, Niko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What else is there to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... if we sold it in a town,\Nmaybe we'd get some money...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even extract oil from one so small,\Nso I don't think it will be worth too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshi-san! I want to eat cutlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make cutlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-We've run out of eggs.\N-Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what should I do with my life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutlet isn't possible, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems the skin is edible too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we make it "demon style"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon style?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There are various theories about\Nthe origin of its name, but
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,its appearence when it's finished\Nlooks like a demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and apparently that's where\Nthe name comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel like I'm cooking a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's small,\Nit does have a proper heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons fly on the sky thanks to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After beheading it and emptying it out,\Nwe slice it down its back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, do it, I'll prepare the marinade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How skillful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just small, but it's the same as\Ndissecting any other dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Olive oil, lemon, salt and pepper,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then, some spices I found in the galley,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and we leave it for 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On a frypan with a generous amount of oil,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we fry it with the skin side down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Irresistible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Press it down with a pot full of water,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and when it gets a good fried colour,\Nflip it and repeat the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the skin side down again,\Nand when it's crispy fried...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Time to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mika! Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mika-san!\N-It had poison after all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! Don't scare us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We caught it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The outside is crispy and aromatic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the inside is so tender\Nthe umami just goes whaam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, you are too much\Nof a glutton always!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't let myself\Nbe blinded by greed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been blinded by it so\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really agree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bring Gibbs-san half of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika, aren't you too blinded by greed\Nafter all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... don't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't found the dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a gift for the royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a really rare ultra-small type\Nthat can be appreciated even indoors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:20:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worth 2 billions! 2 billions!\NDo whatever you need to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's any poison, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Headache, chills, shivers, and fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These symptoms are just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,His exhaustion might caught up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs-san has been working day and night\Nwith barely no relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs works too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try too hard either, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a huge debt to pay off,\Nso I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you in the ship, Jiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For a lot of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not good to keep secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't it good that it's lively?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.95,0:22:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
